# Hexos Multi-Account File
#
# Supported formats (one account per line):
#   email|password
#   email|password|custom_label
#   email:password
#   email;password
#   email<tab>password
#
# Lines starting with # are ignored.
# Each account will be logged in via Google OAuth using Camoufox browser automation.
#
# Usage:
#   hexos auth batch-connect --file accounts.txt --concurrency 2
#
# Tips:
# - Use app-specific passwords if 2FA is enabled on Google
# - Keep concurrency at 2-3 to avoid Google rate limiting
# - Set HEXOS_HEADLESS=false to debug login issues visually

# Pipe delimiter (recommended)
user1@gmail.com|password123
user2@gmail.com|secretpass456
user3@gmail.com|p@ssw0rd789|Production Account

# Colon delimiter also works
user4@gmail.com:mypassword
user5@gmail.com:complex:pass:with:colons

# Semicolon delimiter
user6@gmail.com;anotherpassword
